    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >篮筐战士 是一款多人派对篮球游戏，规则全无，卡通风格画面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与朋友或其他玩家对战，并在最多容纳6人的大厅中得分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/6bdabfe31188766b35925473c8b769fc.poster.avif?t=1766132216\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/6bdabfe31188766b35925473c8b769fc.webm?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/6bdabfe31188766b35925473c8b769fc.mp4?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以拳击、滑向对手，甚至向对方投掷物品来抢夺篮球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记得在得分后赶快跑向篮球，因为游戏永不停歇！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b0b682e8d56251911ee8460ddc9f0849.poster.avif?t=1766132216\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b0b682e8d56251911ee8460ddc9f0849.webm?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b0b682e8d56251911ee8460ddc9f0849.mp4?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款最无规则、最搞笑的篮球游戏中，展示你的篮球技巧，尽情享受无限乐趣，并击败对手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最能展现你心情的角色，跳上球场大显身手吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b484870e366ff0585c0cb37f44d0e3aa.poster.avif?t=1766132216\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b484870e366ff0585c0cb37f44d0e3aa.webm?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244520/extras/b484870e366ff0585c0cb37f44d0e3aa.mp4?t=1766132216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
